data.description: $10,000 CREDIT now being offered on this extraordinarily built home in the desirable 'SHADOW RIDGE" development of Blandon being offered in Very GOOD "as- is" condition. Only three minutes to the 222 corridor for convenient access to both Berks county and Lehigh Valley points. Home consists of expansive kitchen with tile floors, plentiful cabinets and large island work space plus Living, Dining  and family (or office) rooms on main floor. 4 Spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths on 2nd floor. Extra bonus-Finished lower level in basement. Rear deck and landscape all redone just a few months ago. New carpet, windows, garage doors and front door all replaced between four and five years ago. Interior paint approximately five years ago. Rear deck accessible from kitchen, modest yard and 2 car attached garage complete the ensemble. Call for details & schedule your tour today!
